document_data.caption: A map showing Picklock Alley in the Dock Ward of Waterdeep.
document_data.name: Picklock Alley
document_data.mainbody: '''Picklock Alley''' was a small backalley that was located in the city of [[Waterdeep]].{{Cite interactive atlas|Waterdeep}}
document_data.Location: Picklock Alley was connected to [[Gut Alley]] in Waterdeep's [[Waterdeep/Dock Ward|Dock Ward]], branching west just south of the intersection with [[Adder Lane]] and continuing to a dead end after several buildings. [[Julbuck Alley]] branched south off of Picklock Alley.
